prodNameC: 和平類風濕性因子試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.RF Latex Reagent：A suspension of uniform polystyrene particles coated with IgG (human)in glycine buffer,pH8.2;reagent sensitivity is standardized with the World Health Organization RF Standard.
2.RF Positive Control Serum：A stabilized,prediluted human serum containing at least 8 IU/mL of RF.
3.RF Negative Control Serum：A stabilized,prediluted human serum containing less than 8 IU/mL of RF.
4.Glycine-Saline Buffer (20x)：pH8.2±0.1M glycine and 0.15M NaCl.
